961-1 has a variable apearance, except for the eye-holes. So why would they think it was the same entity? Given what they observe, I would conclude that the sundial just applies the empty sockets effect to whoever had the pivotal, lynch-pin position in the events. You might reasonably decide it was the same entity based on what it says to the observers, but that's a no-go since the person addressed doesn't remember anything and the others can't understand it.

